      <title>Nvidia 股价飙升意味着 CEO 基金会必须加倍捐赠</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/nvidia-s-stock-surge-means-ceo-s-foundation-must-double-giving</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英伟达公司 (Nvidia Corp.) 的股价飙升给黄仁勋的慈善基金会带来了挑战：随着股价上涨，基金会需要捐赠的资金也会增加。]]></description>
