      <title>加拿大丰业银行呼吁客户在税收损失销售季节到来前转换交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/scotiabank-urges-switch-trades-ahead-of-tax-loss-selling-season</link>
